  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 119.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第119课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "A True Story.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "一个真实的故事。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "Who called out to the thieves in the dark?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "黑暗中是谁向小偷喊话？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "Do you like stories?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "你喜欢故事吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "I want to tell you a true story.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我想给你讲一个真实的故事。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "It happened to a friend of mine a year ago.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这件事一年前发生在我的一个朋友身上。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "While my friend, George, was reading in bed, two thieves climbed into his kitchen.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我的朋友乔治躺在床上看书时，两个小偷爬进了他的厨房。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "After they had entered the house, they went into the dining room.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他们进入房子后，走进了餐厅。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "It was very dark, so they turned on a torch.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "里面很黑，所以他们打开了一支手电筒。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "Suddenly, they heard a voice behind them.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "突然，他们听到身后有个声音。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "What's up?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“怎么了？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "What's up?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "怎么了？”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "Someone called.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "有人喊道。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "The thieves dropped the torch and ran away as quickly as they could.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "小偷扔下手电筒，飞快地逃走了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "text": "George heard the noise and came downstairs quickly.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "乔治听到响声，迅速下了楼。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "text": "He turned on the light, but he couldn't see anyone.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他打开灯，但一个人也没看见。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "text": "The thieves had already gone.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "小偷早已逃走了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "text": "But George's parrot, Henry, was still there.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "但乔治的鹦鹉亨利还在那里。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "text": "What's up, George?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“怎么了，乔治？”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "text": "He called.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "它叫道。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "text": "Nothing, Henry, George said and smiled.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“没什么，亨利。”乔治笑着说，"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s023",
      "text": "Go back to sleep.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“回去睡觉吧。”"
      }
    }
  ],
